[HEADER]
id: witch_hut
title: Witch's Hut

[CONTENT]
The hut smells of ash, herbs, and river mud.
An old witch stirs a copper cauldron without looking up.
"Traveler," she rasps, "the dead speak loudly in these woods. Drink, and you may hear them."
"Refuse, and I will not be insulted twice."

[OPTIONS]
drink | Drink the potion -> ./cave_entrance.level
refuse | Refuse -> ../endings/death_curse.level

[DIRECTIVES]
input_mode: choice

[OPTION_EFFECTS]
option=drink add_flag=spirit_sight
